{"tid":1679423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"都是英國的錯 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-10-28T07:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:08:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2585a9a2c358e14dc29d47b43d93506664e91c47","tid":1679423,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191028/20794984/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F20794984%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5zKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=859805af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F20794984%2F&h=f4d3962c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191028/20794984/</a><br />\n<br />\n都是英國的錯 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191028/large/1572160686_d3ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572160686_d3ad.jpg&h=2183b801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.sky.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5zKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=b9356afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.sky.com</a>圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國警方在埃塞克斯郡一輛貨櫃車上發現39具屍體，據報道死者有中國人和越南人。《環球時報》總編胡錫進在網絡貼文，提醒世人，「在英國已經不是第一次發生類似驚悚事件了。2000年英國一輛貨車裏有58名中國非法移民在轉運途中被活活悶死。還有2004年英國一個海灘上，23名中國人被海吞沒身亡。」「我不知道這些事件之間有沒有英國社會治理問題上的聯繫，但是這樣的人道主義災難性事件在英國屢現實在讓人無法接受。」<br />\n<br />\n胡總提醒世人，中華人民共和國公民冒死離開盛世強國，一次又一次偷渡去英國做黑巿居民，絕非偶然現象。即使英國多次被揭露人蛇大量死亡事件，都無阻盛世中國公民逃離的決心，寧做英國鬼，不做強國人。胡總問的既不是這些非個別事件與中國社會治理問題上有沒有聯繫，也不是中國公民為甚麼處心積慮背叛那麼好的祖國，而是責問英國出了甚麼問題，邏輯上似乎很是出了點問題。<br />\n<br />\n英國是被動的，英國沒有發出簽證給上述中國人，中國人用非法手段入境英國，怎麼可能責怪英國？當然，千錯萬錯都是別人的錯，正是中國人遇事後的慣常反應。胡總的反應屬正常中國人的反應，世人毋須訝異。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者非常清醒，留言指，「中國那麼好，這些中國人冒死離開中國，就是為了在外國定居，然後歌頌黨和祖國的偉大。」 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"fbf942a149b17ddfd2bcec91dd216c2b0f93ebf5","tid":1679423,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3gbRGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3gbRGC.jpg&h=94dd7b77&s={SIZE}\" />老豆搵仔：新疆單野俾譚仔搞到沉晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676450</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"15a5451aba9e74d7f6e6be93f306316685a2f549","tid":1679423,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:06:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10月31星期四：太子靈堂悼念太子站事件兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />11月2星期六：維園集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ayU5dBt.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/wQNKuag.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"3e2a4bcbf23796f4b791d85a415c501b6d36c404","tid":1679423,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國那麼好，這些中國人冒死離開中國，就是為了在外國定居，然後歌頌黨和祖國的偉大。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}